a joint statement, Mr. President...

259
00:17:54,402 --> 00:17:57,006
threatening military action
to get the North Koreans...

260
00:17:57,007 --> 00:17:59,239
to stand down from the border

261
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:01,719
and stop their missile tests.

262
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,609
Which I think we should give them.

263
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:07,639
Ruth?

264
00:18:07,640 --> 00:18:10,166
Provided that the
North Koreans are rational...

265
00:18:10,167 --> 00:18:11,969
which is dicey, at best.

266
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:16,079
We bluff. They call it. Then what?

267
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:17,809
Well, who says we'd be bluffing?

268
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:21,328
Personally,
I like to try to avoid a war.

269
00:18:22,760 --> 00:18:23,807
Charlie?

270
00:18:24,560 --> 00:18:27,450
I think I agree with Ruth on this one,
Mr. President.

271
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,844
Thank you for sitting in, Mr. Speaker.

272
00:18:30,845 --> 00:18:32,922
- Yes, sir.
- I won't hold you up any longer.

273
00:18:43,800 --> 00:18:45,802
- Hello, Mr. Speaker.
- Hello, Janie.

274
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:48,605
What time is Minister Lee due to arrive?

275
00:18:48,606 --> 00:18:50,090
7:00 this evening.

276
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:09,010
Our guests have arrived.

277
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,879
Prime Minister Lee.

278
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,639
I'm Special Agent-in-Charge Roma.

279
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:37,210
I'd like to welcome you
to the White House, sir.

280
00:20:37,211 --> 00:20:37,845
Thank you.

281
00:20:37,846 --> 00:20:40,923
May I introduce my Head of Security
and Chief Aide, Mr. Park.

282
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:44,651
My pleasure.
Prime Minister, after you, please.

283
00:20:50,120 --> 00:20:53,124
Agent Davis will be taking care
of your security team outside.

284
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,885
Prime Minister, if you would follow
Agent O'Neil, please?

285
00:20:58,200 --> 00:20:59,122
Ma.
Am?

286
00:21:01,520 --> 00:21:03,202
Private sector looks good on you, Dave.

287
00:21:03,203 --> 00:21:04,770
Yeah, something to look forward to.

288
00:21:04,771 --> 00:21:06,719
Yeah. How've you been?

289
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,562
I'll tell you.
I miss the Secret Service.

290
00:21:08,563 --> 00:21:09,971
Best years of my life.

291
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:12,399
It misses you too, old man.

292
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,890
I could still kick your ass.

293
00:21:14,680 --> 00:21:16,603
At what? Dominos?

294
00:21:17,560 --> 00:21:19,608
- It's good to see you, my friend.
- You, too.

295
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:33,921
Unidentified flight,

296
00:21:33,922 --> 00:21:37,204
this is Flight Leader, U.S. Air
Force aircraft at your starboard wing.

297
00:21:37,205 --> 00:21:38,929
You've entered restricted airspace.

298
00:21:39,320 --> 00:21:40,401
Unidentified flight,

299
00:21:40,402 --> 00:21:43,924
you must divert immediately
to vector 0-2-0. Acknowledge.

300
00:21:43,925 --> 00:21:46,204
I'm sorry to have
disrupted your vacation.

301
00:21:46,205 --> 00:21:47,690
Please. I'm glad you could come.

302
00:21:48,200 --> 00:21:50,328
Mr. Lee, we have a mutual problem.

303
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:54,124
And I think together,
I'm confident we can find a solution.

304
00:21:54,125 --> 00:21:57,010
Thank you, Mr. President.
That's why I'm here.

305
00:21:57,560 --> 00:22:00,445
As you know, North Korea
has a one million man standing army...

306
00:22:00,446 --> 00:22:02,681
less than 50 kilometers
from our capital.

307
00:22:03,040 --> 00:22:04,246
The threat is real.

308
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,604
Unidentified flight.

309
00:22:07,605 --> 00:22:10,166
You must divert immediately
to vector 0-2-0.

310
00:22:10,167 --> 00:22:13,403
This is your final warning.
You will be shot down. Acknowledge.

311
00:22:21,280 --> 00:22:23,328
Anti-aircraft. We're taking fire.

312
00:22:37,120 --> 00:22:39,120
Mr. Lee, I'm sure you can appreciate
that this is...

313
00:22:39,121 --> 00:22:40,804
Sir? There's been an incursion.
Please stand up.

314
00:22:40,805 --> 00:22:41,767
Let's go. Move!

315
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:44,921
- Mr. Lee, please join us.
- That's not protocol, sir.

316
00:22:44,922 --> 00:22:45,724
He's coming with us!

317
00:22:45,725 --> 00:22:47,688
Move, move, move!
Get him to the elevator.

318
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,163
- Go! Go!
- Find Connor!

319
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:53,279
Code 9-9-9.

320
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:54,611
Go, go, go! Move!

321
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,481
Keep moving!
Get that elevator open now!

322
00:23:04,320 --> 00:23:06,002
Give me four minutes, Mr. President.

323
00:23:06,003 --> 00:23:07,365
Harden down on Olympus.

324
00:23:11,760 --> 00:23:13,285
Air support on the way.

325
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,799
ETA, four minutes.

326
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:21,009
Code Red. Air space 1 and 2 compromised.

327
00:23:21,600 --> 00:23:23,245
Robert, Delta, Ready One.

328
00:23:23,246 --> 00:23:26,210
Move to West Corridor!
Move to West Corridor!

329
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,159
This way, please.

330
00:23:43,160 --> 00:23:45,766
This is not a drill.
Evacuate immediately.

331
00:24:13,800 --> 00:24:16,239
All units, 9-9-9.

332
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:19,881
I repeat, all units, 9-9-9.

333
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:06,327
Let's move!

334
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,407
Find my son.

335
00:25:13,880 --> 00:25:15,211
Sylvio, find Sparkplug immediately.

336
00:25:15,212 --> 00:25:16,440
You okay, Mr. President?

337
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:19,325
Sir. This way. Over here.

338
00:25:24,840 --> 00:25:26,729
Go on! Get down!

339
00:25:29,560 --> 00:25:30,243
Get down!

340
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,324
Stay down! Don't move!

341
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:49,009
Get down! Get out of the way!
Take cover!

342
00:26:18,120 --> 00:26:21,567
PPD Command, this is Wolfhound 6.
Have bogey in sight.

343
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:24,771
Wolfhound 6, fire at will.
Repeat, fire at will.

344
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,241
Acknowledge.

345
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:26,927
Mr. President?

346
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:31,001
We have confirmation
that the bogey is down, sir.

347
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:32,600
Thank you, Jones.

348
00:27:35,080 --> 00:27:36,799
Activate Compound One.

349
00:27:36,800 --> 00:27:40,247
I want open lines to the Pentagon,
Homeland Security and NSA.

350
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:44,245
Charlie.
Coordinate with the Air Force and FAA.

351
00:27:44,246 --> 00:27:46,763
- Find out if that's' a lone aircraft.
- Yes, sir.

352
00:27:46,764 --> 00:27:48,046
Half hour at the most.

353
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,848
Ruth. Where the hell is my son?

354
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,007
Hey!

355
00:28:35,960 --> 00:28:37,399
Hey!

356
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:39,209
Hey, get the fuck down!

357
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:42,879
Mr. Lee. We've had a problem.

358
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:44,723
- Please have patience with us.
- Got it.

359
00:29:44,724 --> 00:29:46,449
- Mr. President.
- Yes?

360
00:29:48,600 --> 00:29:49,965
It's a critical message.

361
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:54,249
The White House is under ground attack.

362
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:22,644
Officer on deck!

363
00:30:22,645 --> 00:30:25,450
Rapid Response Team from Andrews,
get 'em moving!

364
00:30:25,451 --> 00:30:27,679
At ease. How bad is it?

365
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:29,165
Front fence has been breached.

366
00:30:29,166 --> 00:30:31,161
We've got a C-130 burning
on the South Lawn

367
00:30:31,162 --> 00:30:33,003
and a gunfight raging on the North.

368
00:30:33,004 --> 00:30:34,879
Fucking shitting me.

369
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:36,206
Where's the president?

370
00:30:36,207 --> 00:30:37,087
In the bunker.

371
00:31:12,080 --> 00:31:14,364
- Get me the Pentagon on the line now!
- Yes, sir!

372
00:31:14,365 --> 00:31:15,361
It's happening.

373
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,641
Mr. President!

374
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:35,006
Forbes, what are you doing?

375
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:39,041
- Move!
- For God's sakes, Forbes.

376
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:47,884
Forbes! What are you doing?

377
00:31:48,320 --> 00:31:49,082
Shut up!

378
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,079
Come on. Tim.

379
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:51,879
Come on. Hang in there!

380
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,767
Hey!

381
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:55,121
Ah, shit.

382
00:33:00,520 --> 00:33:01,759
Where's the president?

383
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:02,921
I don't know!

384
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:06,241
Goddamn it! Where's that response team?

385
00:33:06,242 --> 00:33:08,719
- They're 5 minutes out, sir, but...
- But what?

386
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:11,121
We have a hostage situation
on our hands.

387
00:33:11,122 --> 00:33:12,849
P.E.O.C.'s gone offline.

388
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:40,686
Go back! Get back now! Go back!

389
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,446
Fuck!

390
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:25,965
RPG!

391
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:38,406
Get in! Get inside! Get inside!

392
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:52,248
Come on! Come on! Come on! Come on!

393
00:36:07,640 --> 00:36:09,210
Go, go! Move!

394
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,199
Fall back, fall back!

395
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,565
Let's go, let's go!

396
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:24,687
- They're down the hall!
- Shit, we've only got four guys left!

397
00:36:24,688 --> 00:36:26,330
Hold your positions, you understand?

398
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:32,923
I got this door. Cover the other one.

399
00:36:55,720 --> 00:36:58,599
Olympus has fallen. Olympus has fallen.

400
00:36:58,600 --> 00:37:00,125
Olympus has fallen.

401
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:02,967
Fuck you!

402
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:09,964
They've taken the White House.

403
00:37:38,120 --> 00:37:40,088
Command, Sniper Team One, in position.

404
00:38:02,360 --> 00:38:04,931
We're coming from the White House.
So far, the perimeter's been set.

405
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:07,605
We're waiting on more intel to come
in right now, and once we do...

406
00:38:07,606 --> 00:38:09,245
Bravo team's gonna breach.

407
00:38:09,246 --> 00:38:11,891
- Wait for my command to execute.
- Yes, sir.

408
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:17,886
Not since the British burned down
the White House in the War of 1812...

409
00:38:17,887 --> 00:38:21,085
has an enemy force occupied
the center of American power.

410
00:38:21,086 --> 00:38:21,922
The White House,

411
00:38:21,923 --> 00:38:25,606
the most protected building on Earth,
has fallen.

412
00:38:26,080 --> 00:38:28,401
Sir,
we have a hot feed from the P.E.O.C.

413
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:33,359
Mr. Lee. Sir, are you safe?

414
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:35,089
Are you with the president?

415
00:38:35,090 --> 00:38:36,764
Sir, can you hear m...?

416
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:38,881
Oh, my God.

417
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,291
Don't negotiate.

418
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:51,766
Sir?

419
00:38:52,080 --> 00:38:54,242
I have your commander-in-chief.

420
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:57,410
Now, stand down.

421
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:59,199
Who are you?

422
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:01,965
I am the man in control
of your White House.

423
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:07,050
Now, stand your men down.

424
00:39:14,200 --> 00:39:15,559
- Stand down!
- Sir.

425
00:39:15,560 --> 00:39:17,369
All units, stand down!

426
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:21,399
Ladies and gentlemen we are at DEFCON 4.

427
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,731
How could you?

428
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,921
- Put your hands up.
- Fuck you.

429
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:40,371
No!

430
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,442
There is a reason I never voted for you.

431
00:39:53,720 --> 00:39:55,085
Don't do it, Forbes!

432
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:50,725
It takes 15 minutes
for your Armed Forces

433
00:41:50,726 --> 00:41:52,245
to reach the White House.

434
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:56,609
We took it down in 13.

435
00:43:34,080 --> 00:43:35,125
Hurry, we need a wheelchair.

436
00:43:35,126 --> 00:43:37,726
In Triage, do you want me
to color code them or number code them?

437
00:43:37,727 --> 00:43:38,641
Color code 'em.

438
00:43:38,642 --> 00:43:40,722
Okay, Pam,
we still need to take the vitals.

439
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:53,446
Call, Mike. Mike.

440
00:43:56,920 --> 00:43:59,279
The cellular service in the area
you are calling

441
00:43:59,280 --> 00:44:00,247
has been suspended temporarily.

442
00:44:00,248 --> 00:44:02,846
I got head trauma,
six-year-old girl, she's fading!

443
00:44:20,720 --> 00:44:22,290
Bring Mr. Asher here.

444
00:44:24,520 --> 00:44:26,602
What are you doing, for Christ's sake?

445
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:30,406
Oh, sir!

446
00:44:33,600 --> 00:44:36,410
I have no interest
in your nuclear launch codes.

447
00:44:38,840 --> 00:44:41,605
By now your Pentagon
has changed then, no?

448
00:44:42,840 --> 00:44:44,171
Sit.

449
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:46,331
You from the North?

450
00:44:46,960 --> 00:44:48,928
You sure as hell are not from the South.

451
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:51,329
I'm working for justice.

452
00:44:51,640 --> 00:44:54,163
To give millions of starving
men, women and children

453
00:44:54,164 --> 00:44:56,683
a chance at more than just subsistence.

454
00:44:56,684 --> 00:45:00,401
To end the civil war your country
interrupted so long ago.

455
00:45:01,160 --> 00:45:02,446
And yes...

456
00:45:04,360 --> 00:45:06,799
for a united, prosperous Korea.

457
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:08,723
It's a whole new world, baby.

458
00:45:09,280 --> 00:45:11,681
What's the going rate for souls
these days?

459
00:45:12,440 --> 00:45:13,679
What'd you say to me?

460
00:45:13,680 --> 00:45:15,409
I never would have taken you
for a traitor.

461
00:45:15,410 --> 00:45:16,367
Me?

462
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,599
What about you?

463
00:45:18,600 --> 00:45:21,729
You sold this country out long
before I ever did.

464
00:45:22,080 --> 00:45:25,879
Globalization and fucking Wall Street.

465
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:28,929
What's it cost to buy
a presidency nowadays anyway?

466
00:45:29,440 --> 00:45:32,399
$500 million?

467
00:45:32,400 --> 00:45:36,325
I'm a fucking rookie compared to you!

468
00:45:37,640 --> 00:45:39,449
Gotta keep your gloves up, Forbes.

469
00:45:40,600 --> 00:45:41,442
Enough!

470
00:45:46,120 --> 00:45:47,690
What about Connor?

471
00:45:48,120 --> 00:45:50,009
What the fuck are you gonna do
with my son?

472
00:46:02,680 --> 00:46:03,761
Mr. Speaker.

473
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:06,922
As both the President
and the Vice President

474
00:46:06,923 --> 00:46:09,001
of the United States
are unable to discharge

475
00:46:09,002 --> 00:46:10,443
the duties of their offices

476
00:46:10,444 --> 00:46:14,240
I'm officially placing you
under Secret Service protection.

477
00:46:18,680 --> 00:46:21,604
You are the Acting President
of the United States.

478
00:46:23,680 --> 00:46:24,920
Are they alive?

479
00:46:25,400 --> 00:46:26,561
They are.

480
00:46:37,840 --> 00:46:41,763
Sir, North Korea is denying
any involvement in the attack.

481
00:46:41,764 --> 00:46:44,326
We've secured the perimeter
of the White House...

482
00:46:44,327 --> 00:46:46,205
and cleared a 10-block radius.

483
00:46:46,206 --> 00:46:50,046
Sir, they've also assassinated
the South Korean Prime Minister.

484
00:47:57,880 --> 00:48:00,526
We have contact
from inside the White House.

485
00:48:00,527 --> 00:48:02,921
Trace confirms
it's the president's Sat phone.

486
00:48:03,240 --> 00:48:04,207
Put it through!

487
00:48:05,360 --> 00:48:06,771
Mr. President?

488
00:48:07,080 --> 00:48:08,519
Negative.

489
00:48:08,520 --> 00:48:10,999
- Identify yourself.
- Echelon Four.

490
00:48:11,000 --> 00:48:12,001
That's one of yours?

491
00:48:12,002 --> 00:48:16,319
- Designator?
- Oscar Zulu 309.

492
00:48:16,320 --> 00:48:19,039
Jesus. Banning? Where are you?

493
00:48:19,040 --> 00:48:20,639
I'm in the Oval Office.

494
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,290
Is the president in the bunker?

495
00:48:22,291 --> 00:48:24,886
- He...
- Can we trust him?

496
00:48:25,760 --> 00:48:27,884
Banning was one of our best agents.

497
00:48:27,885 --> 00:48:30,319
Mr. Speaker, I just have to say,
this is Mike Banning.

498
00:48:30,320 --> 00:48:32,799
This is the same guy that was removed
from the president's detail...

499
00:48:32,800 --> 00:48:33,720
- after the accident
- Whoa, whoa,

500
00:48:33,721 --> 00:48:34,959
- when we lost the first lady?
- Ray! Ray! Ray!

501
00:48:34,960 --> 00:48:35,959
- You wanna add something?
- Well, what's he doing

502
00:48:35,960 --> 00:48:36,766
- I suggest you get your facts straight.
- In the White House right now?

503
00:48:36,767 --> 00:48:38,285
- How do we know we can trust this guy?

504
00:48:38,286 --> 00:48:41,090
Banning is ex-Special Forces,
Ranger Battalion

505
00:48:41,091 --> 00:48:45,130
He will move mountains or die try.
I know him.

506
00:48:45,600 --> 00:48:46,803
Does anyone else in this room

507
00:48:46,804 --> 00:48:49,531
have any intelligence
coming out of the White House?

508
00:48:51,400 --> 00:48:52,925
Then we have no choice.

509
00:48:54,760 --> 00:48:58,560
Yes. The president's in the bunker.
He's being held hostage.

510
00:49:00,120 --> 00:49:01,323
What do they want?

511
00:49:01,324 --> 00:49:02,765
We're trying to find out.

512
00:49:03,160 --> 00:49:04,519
Who's in charge?

513
00:49:04,520 --> 00:49:05,439
Trumbull.

514
00:49:05,440 --> 00:49:08,011
- Are there any survivors with you?
- Negative, sir.

515
00:49:08,760 --> 00:49:10,091
They wiped us out.

516
00:49:12,160 --> 00:49:14,444
They have commandos roaming
the hallways...

517
00:49:14,445 --> 00:49:16,807
with enough explosives
to take out an army.

518
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:20,839
Looks like the doors and windows
are rigged with C-4 explosives.

519
00:49:20,840 --> 00:49:23,081
Who knows what other tricks
they have up their sleeves?

520
00:49:23,640 --> 00:49:26,803
Any team coming in is gonna be ringing
the front doorbell pretty loud.

521
00:49:27,400 --> 00:49:28,639
They shut the power down.

522
00:49:28,640 --> 00:49:31,086
Lights off.
And I assume they closed the air vents.

523
00:49:31,520 --> 00:49:32,442
I killed the surveillance,

524
00:49:32,443 --> 00:49:34,647
but I don't know
how long that's gonna last.

525
00:49:34,648 --> 00:49:35,687
Where's Connor?

526
00:49:36,200 --> 00:49:40,325
Oh, we have no status of his location,
but he's presumed to still be inside.

527
00:49:40,326 --> 00:49:42,082
Well, they're looking for him.

528
00:49:42,083 --> 00:49:43,411
