529
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:45,166
Sir...

530
00:49:45,880 --> 00:49:47,599
I'm here. Use me.

531
00:49:47,600 --> 00:49:50,649
Okay, Banning. Sit tight.
We'll get back with you.

532
00:50:48,280 --> 00:50:50,442
