- What is it you want?

534
00:50:53,680 --> 00:50:56,604
Recall the Seventh Fleet
from the Sea of Japan.

535
00:50:56,605 --> 00:51:01,559
And withdraw all 28,500 American troops
from the Demilitarized Zone.

536
00:51:01,560 --> 00:51:03,210
