541
00:51:15,240 --> 00:51:17,321
and their blood will be on your hands.

542
00:51:17,322 --> 00:51:18,651
You have until dawn.

543
00:51:18,960 --> 00:51:20,883
I suggest you move quickly.

544
00:51:22,800 --> 00:51:23,641
Who is that guy?

545
00:51:23,642 --> 00:51:26,286
Well, sir, we're running facial
recognition on him right now.

546
00:51:26,287 --> 00:51:29,045
Well, he cleared as part of
the South Korean security detail.

547
00:51:29,046 --> 00:51:32,679
If we recall the Fleet,
and leave the DMZ...

548
00:51:32,680 --> 00:51:36,161
Seoul, all of South Korea could fall
within 72 hours, sir.

549
00:51:36,162 --> 00:51:39,242
But if we do nothing, they kill Asher,
the vice president...

550
00:51:39,243 --> 00:51:41,208
and his entire National Security team.

551
00:51:41,209 --> 00:51:43,328
And Connor, if he's in there.

552
00:51:58,920 --> 00:52:00,639
Mary, get me some coffee

553
00:52:00,640 --> 00:52:04,439
Half-and-half, three Sweet 'N Lows.
In a real cup.

554
00:52:04,440 --> 00:52:06,727
Not one of those paper
or Styrofoam things.

555
00:52:09,200 --> 00:52:13,159
All right.
Let's secure all nuclear sites.

556
00:52:13,160 --> 00:52:15,519
Get me our expert on North Korea.

557
00:52:15,520 --> 00:52:18,841
Then I want to speak with the Premiere
