558
00:52:18,842 --> 00:52:20,682
After that,
I wanna speak with the Russians,

559
00:52:20,683 --> 00:52:22,644
the Chinese,
the British and the French.

560
00:52:22,645 --> 00:52:24,927
And set up a press conference.
In that order.

561
00:52:28,840 --> 00:52:32,049
The United States of America
doesn't negotiate with terrorists.

562
00:52:38,600 --> 00:52:41,285
Who said anything about negotiating?

563
00:53:09,160 --> 00:53:13,290
Admiral Hoenig, your Cerberus code.

564
00:53:19,960 --> 00:53:21,962
You kill him, you won't get the code.

565
00:53:23,200 --> 00:53:25,168
I will not ask again.

566
00:53:45,280 --> 00:53:48,011
- Give it to him, Joe.
- Mr. President.

567
00:53:48,440 --> 00:53:49,965
You'll never get mine.

568
00:53:50,760 --> 00:53:55,971
Tango-Juliet-1-9-3-3-4.

569
00:53:57,880 --> 00:53:59,079
Louder.

570
00:53:59,080 --> 00:54:04,086
Tango-Juliet-1-9-3-3-4.

571
00:54:16,160 --> 00:54:17,400
What the hell?

572
00:54:18,600 --> 00:54:20,204
Get me Homeland Security.

573
00:54:20,205 --> 00:54:21,167
No, now!

574
00:54:25,040 --> 00:54:29,364
Sir. NORAD reports a Cerberus code
