and pull our troops out.

588
00:55:11,000 --> 00:55:12,126
Oh, is that all?

589
00:55:13,440 --> 00:55:15,841
A Cerberus code has been entered.

590
00:55:16,560 --> 00:55:17,959
What's Cerberus?

591
00:55:17,960 --> 00:55:19,279
That's classified.

592
00:55:19,280 --> 00:55:20,964
Classified? Really?

593
00:55:21,400 --> 00:55:24,643
Well, right now I think I have
the proverbial need-to-fucking-know.

594
00:55:29,400 --> 00:55:32,643
Cerberus is a
highly-classified military protocol.

595
00:55:33,000 --> 00:55:38,006
A 3-pronged fail-safe in the case of
an inadvertent nuclear launch.

596
00:55:39,160 --> 00:55:42,639
It allows us to access
the self-destruct mechanism

597
00:55:42,640 --> 00:55:45,079
in our ICBM's in-flight.

598
00:55:45,080 --> 00:55:48,205
So even if one of our nuclear warheads
was launched and we wanted to abort.

599
00:55:48,206 --> 00:55:51,329
Cerberus is the only way to stop it
from reaching its target.

600
00:55:51,330 --> 00:55:53,687
No one person has all three codes.

601
00:55:54,120 --> 00:55:57,325
It's parceled out to the president,
Secretary of Defense...

602
00:55:57,326 --> 00:55:59,321
and the Chairman of the Joint Chiefs.

603
00:55:59,322 --> 00:56:02,085
All of whom are
in the president's bunker right now.

604
00:56:02,086 --> 00:56:05,879
With those codes they can destroy
any long-reach nuke that we fire.

605
00:56:05,880 --> 00:56:09,771
And that would make America vulnerable
to a nuclear strike.

606
00:56:11,400 --> 00:56:12,999
So, change the codes.

607
00:56:13,000 --> 00:56:14,079
We can't.

608
00:56:14,080 --> 00:56:16,044
Cerberus was designed
as a self-contained

609
00:56:16,045 --> 00:56:17,525
total-isolation system.

610
00:56:17,526 --> 00:56:20,565
The only way to change the codes
is physically on the computer itself.

611
00:56:20,566 --> 00:56:22,801
Which is located
in the president's bunker.

612
00:56:22,802 --> 00:56:25,323
So, now we know why
they wanted the president's son.

613
00:56:25,324 --> 00:56:27,923
The president will hold out
as long as he can.

614
00:56:27,924 --> 00:56:29,570
But if they get his son...

615
