730
01:09:36,200 --> 01:09:38,280
Well, Jesus Christ,
nobody ever thought to look for him

731
01:09:38,281 --> 01:09:39,406
inside the South Korean government.

732
01:09:39,407 --> 01:09:42,210
Look, I don't care who he is.
With a force that size

