772
01:12:47,800 --> 01:12:48,767
Ruth!

773
01:12:53,640 --> 01:12:54,766
Your code!

774
01:12:55,840 --> 01:12:57,719
You'll have to kill me.

775
01:12:57,720 --> 01:12:59,165
As you wish.

776
01:13:08,160 --> 01:13:09,525
There's a saying...

777
01:13:10,560 --> 01:13:11,686
in Korea.

778
01:13:17,520 --> 01:13:19,405
Seeing something a 100 times...

779
01:13:19,406 --> 01:13:21,528
is not as good as living it once.

780
01:13:23,640 --> 01:13:24,971
Fuck you.

781
01:13:26,240 --> 01:13:27,287
Stop!

782
01:13:27,840 --> 01:13:29,319
Enough!

783
01:13:29,320 --> 01:13:30,924
Enough! Stop!

784
01:13:33,160 --> 01:13:34,127
Enough!

785
01:13:45,000 --> 01:13:46,411
Give it to him, Ruth.

786
01:13:47,000 --> 01:13:48,319
It doesn't matter.

787
01:13:48,320 --> 01:13:50,004
And he won't get mine.

788
01:13:55,520 --> 01:13:56,362
Ruth.

789
01:14:01,920 --> 01:14:03,126
Give it to him!

790
01:14:04,160 --> 01:14:05,844
That's an order, Ruth.

791
01:14:06,400 --> 01:14:07,526
Sir...

792
01:14:08,360 --> 01:14:09,930
Give it him, Ruth.

793
01:14:12,160 --> 01:14:13,605
Yes, sir.

794
01:14:15,720 --> 01:14:19,559
Echo-Mike...

795
01:14:19,560 --> 01:14:24,168
6-0-2-8...

796
01:14:25,440 --> 01:14:27,920
5, sir.

797
01:14:35,960 --> 01:14:39,965
Get your fucking hands off of me!

798
01:14:42,680 --> 01:14:46,685
Sir, NORAD reports that the second
Cerberus code has been entered.

799
01:14:52,400 --> 01:14:53,401
My God.

800
01:15:06,200 --> 01:15:09,359
- Mike! Mike, Mike, it's me.
- Dave?

801
01:15:09,360 --> 01:15:10,845
You scared the shit out of me.

802
01:15:10,846 --> 01:15:12,079
Jesus, what the fuck?

803
01:15:12,080 --> 01:15:12,886
Yeah, just put that thing down.

804
01:15:12,887 --> 01:15:14,564
I almost blew your
fucking brains out, man.

805
01:15:14,565 --> 01:15:15,763
What are you doing here?

806
01:15:15,764 --> 01:15:17,682
I was with the South Korean delegation.

807
01:15:17,683 --> 01:15:19,719
What the fuck are you doing here?

808
01:15:19,720 --> 01:15:21,085
I thought you were working
at the Treasury.

809
01:15:21,086 --> 01:15:22,239
Yeah, I am.

810
01:15:22,240 --> 01:15:24,288
Believe it or not,
I came in through the front door.

811
01:15:25,760 --> 01:15:29,367
Oh, fuck, Mike.

812
01:15:29,800 --> 01:15:31,882
I saw my life flash in front of me.

813
01:15:31,883 --> 01:15:34,679
Look at my hand. Fucker's shakin'.

814
01:15:34,680 --> 01:15:35,999
Jesus Christ.

815
01:15:36,000 --> 01:15:37,363
It's good to see you, buddy.

816
01:15:37,364 --> 01:15:39,044
You got a funny way of showing it.

817
01:15:43,240 --> 01:15:44,526
Is the president okay?

818
01:15:44,527 --> 01:15:45,851
He's alive for now.

819
01:15:47,840 --> 01:15:49,365
They got him in the bunker.

820
01:15:50,840 --> 01:15:52,363
It's a fucking shit show, huh?

821
01:15:52,364 --> 01:15:53,691
Yeah, that's for sure.

822
01:15:56,000 --> 01:15:57,331
Roma make it?

823
01:15:59,640 --> 01:16:00,926
Fuck.

824
01:16:02,040 --> 01:16:03,371
We gotta keep movin'.

825
01:16:08,680 --> 01:16:10,602
- You got a plan, Mike?
- Yeah.

826
01:16:10,603 --> 01:16:12,329
But it hasn't worked out so far.

827
01:16:14,440 --> 01:16:16,727
Fuckin' Mike. You always were a hardass.

828
01:16:16,728 --> 01:16:18,210
You never change.

829
01:16:21,200 --> 01:16:22,406
Hey, Dave.

830
01:16:23,160 --> 01:16:26,721
This place is getting me rattled, man.
I can't think straight.

831
01:16:27,520 --> 01:16:28,726
You Okay?

832
01:16:29,600 --> 01:16:32,809
No. Not for real.

833
01:16:33,440 --> 01:16:35,727
This fucking Kang, man. He's crazy.

834
01:16:38,000 --> 01:16:39,411
How do you know his name?

835
01:16:45,880 --> 01:16:48,451
Hey, Mike, do you remember that time
in New York?

836
01:17:44,800 --> 01:17:45,881
Dave.

837
01:17:48,120 --> 01:17:49,451
Why'd you do it?

838
01:17:50,760 --> 01:17:52,569
Fuck, Mike.

839
01:17:54,080 --> 01:17:55,241
Fuck.

840
01:17:57,800 --> 01:17:59,643
I lost my way.

841
01:18:04,240 --> 01:18:06,004
You can make up for it now.

842
01:18:09,080 --> 01:18:10,730
Tell Kang I'm dead.

843
01:18:12,120 --> 01:18:14,043
You'll help me save the president.

844
01:18:18,400 --> 01:18:21,927
Kang. It's Forbes.

845
01:18:23,440 --> 01:18:27,923
I got him. All clear.

846
01:18:30,120 --> 01:18:31,121
Good.

847
01:18:44,960 --> 01:18:46,041
Ruth.

848
01:18:47,240 --> 01:18:49,846
Mr. President, sir?

849
01:18:53,160 --> 01:18:54,321
Rough day.

850
01:18:55,000 --> 01:18:56,445
Could be worse.

851
01:18:57,800 --> 01:18:59,564
How's my hair?

852
01:19:01,440 --> 01:19:03,408
Not a strand out of place.

853
01:19:11,280 --> 01:19:12,611
Any regrets?

854
01:19:12,880 --> 01:19:13,881
None.

855
01:19:15,600 --> 01:19:16,840
You?

856
01:19:19,200 --> 01:19:20,406
A few.

857
01:19:20,880 --> 01:19:22,450
Like running for president.

858
01:19:24,440 --> 01:19:27,205
The office is lucky to have you, sir.

859
01:19:28,320 --> 01:19:31,005
We all may meet our maker today...

860
01:19:33,040 --> 01:19:37,045
but the one thing
I do not want on my tombstone...

861
01:19:38,360 --> 01:19:40,761
"She Went Down Without a Fight."

862
01:19:46,520 --> 01:19:48,010
No danger of that.

863
01:19:49,960 --> 01:19:51,325
Pull up your satellite feed.

864
01:19:52,000 --> 01:19:53,286
Give me eyes on.

865
01:19:55,000 --> 01:19:57,810
Looks like there's only four sentries
on the roof.

866
01:19:58,240 --> 01:19:59,922
With the Air Defense grid gone,

867
01:19:59,923 --> 01:20:01,888
they're vulnerable
to an aerial insertion.

868
01:20:03,200 --> 01:20:05,441
Wait. Let me get there first
and check it out.

869
01:20:06,760 --> 01:20:08,119
We're not waiting.

870
01:20:08,120 --> 01:20:10,009
We have to secure Cerberus.

871
01:20:10,400 --> 01:20:11,811
Oh, fuck.

872
01:20:13,000 --> 01:20:14,843
Send in the SEALS, General.

873
01:20:15,520 --> 01:20:16,851
We're going through the roof.

874
01:20:25,560 --> 01:20:27,289
Command, Tiger Flight inbound.

875
01:20:29,840 --> 01:20:31,251
Tiger Team, stand by.

876
01:20:34,120 --> 01:20:35,882
The assault team is on the way.

877
01:20:35,883 --> 01:20:37,166
About fucking time.

878
01:20:38,280 --> 01:20:39,964
Yes, sir. Copy.

879
01:20:56,760 --> 01:20:59,331
Command,
Tiger Flight's three minutes out.

880
01:20:59,332 --> 01:21:00,845
Team, go green.

881
01:21:01,320 --> 01:21:02,242
Go green.

882
01:21:08,360 --> 01:21:09,009
Cho.

883
01:21:44,920 --> 01:21:48,083
60 seconds to target.
I want a clean deployment.

884
01:22:11,080 --> 01:22:11,842
Fuck.

885
01:22:12,600 --> 01:22:13,647
Tell them to hold.

886
01:22:14,160 --> 01:22:15,889
We aren't holding shit!

887
01:22:17,000 --> 01:22:20,079
Jacobs. You've gotta abort his mission.

888
01:22:20,080 --> 01:22:21,879
They've got the Hydra Six!

889
01:22:21,880 --> 01:22:22,799
What's that?

890
01:22:22,800 --> 01:22:25,039
Next generation weaponry. Ours.

891
01:22:25,040 --> 01:22:27,202
How the hell would they get that?

892
01:22:27,203 --> 01:22:29,282
It doesn't matter.
We'll take it out.

893
01:22:29,920 --> 01:22:31,888
I said abort this fucking mission!

894
01:22:32,400 --> 01:22:34,322
Let's go get our goddamn house back,
Captain.

895
01:22:34,323 --> 01:22:36,687
Tiger Two, Tiger Three,
you're cleared hot.

896
01:22:36,688 --> 01:22:37,879
Tiger Two, roger.

897
01:22:37,880 --> 01:22:39,163
Tiger Three, roger.

898
01:22:39,164 --> 01:22:42,130
All birds, be on the lookout
for possible advanced weaponry.

899
01:22:58,240 --> 01:22:59,765
Approaching rooftop.

900
01:23:02,600 --> 01:23:04,125
Negative on the four sentries.

901
01:23:04,520 --> 01:23:05,806
Tiger Flight's on station.

902
01:23:06,400 --> 01:23:07,367
We got 'em.

903
01:23:08,280 --> 01:23:09,406
Go, go, go!

904
01:23:09,840 --> 01:23:11,444
Fast ropes deployed.

905
01:23:13,960 --> 01:23:16,361
We have a radar locked sourced
from target.

906
01:23:17,920 --> 01:23:19,682
Tiger Two's taking fire
from the rooftop!

907
01:23:19,683 --> 01:23:21,165
Tiger Team, go combat flight.

908
01:23:21,166 --> 01:23:23,002
Tiger Two's hit.He's going down.

909
01:23:23,003 --> 01:23:24,326
Tiger Two going down hard.

910
01:23:24,327 --> 01:23:25,401
Tiger Two's hit.

911
01:23:26,240 --> 01:23:27,284
Evasive, evasive.

912
01:23:27,285 --> 01:23:28,566
Take out that target.

913
01:23:29,160 --> 01:23:30,605
Concentrate fire on that rooftop.

914
01:23:32,400 --> 01:23:34,285
Tiger Three, fly behind the target.

915
01:23:34,286 --> 01:23:35,643
Tiger Four, adjust approach!

916
01:23:35,644 --> 01:23:37,449
Head northwest and flank from there!

917
01:23:39,200 --> 01:23:42,601
Tiger Five and Six, switch to Formation
Charlie and take out that gun!

918
01:23:42,602 --> 01:23:43,965
Damn it, drop altitude!

919
01:23:45,840 --> 01:23:47,444
Tiger One gunner just got hit!

920
01:23:55,280 --> 01:23:56,884
Watch your three. Watch your three.

921
01:23:57,280 --> 01:23:58,247
Taking fire.

922
01:23:58,640 --> 01:23:59,926
- Hold on!
- We're getting hit!

923
01:24:06,040 --> 01:24:07,201
Tiger Six is down!

924
01:24:10,920 --> 01:24:12,081
Tiger Five taking...

925
01:24:15,120 --> 01:24:16,610
Tiger Five's gone down.

926
01:24:18,960 --> 01:24:21,327
Reset formation. Tiger One taking lead.

927
01:24:21,328 --> 01:24:22,367
Roger that.

928
01:24:30,320 --> 01:24:31,401
We need backup!

929
01:24:32,320 --> 01:24:33,162
They're chewing us up!

930
01:24:33,163 --> 01:24:34,885
Engaging Target. Provide cover.

931
01:24:34,886 --> 01:24:36,928
All remaining Blackhawks,
provide air cover.

932
01:24:44,360 --> 01:24:46,806
Two birds up. Only two birds remain.

933
01:24:46,807 --> 01:24:47,959
Abort! Abort!

934
01:24:47,960 --> 01:24:49,083
Pull out. Clear the area.

935
01:24:49,084 --> 01:24:50,605
Roger! Clearing the area!

936
01:24:53,360 --> 01:24:55,249
Tiger One is hit! Losing control!

937
01:24:59,440 --> 01:25:02,762
Tail rotor failure.
Mayday, mayday! We're going down!

938
01:25:32,640 --> 01:25:34,324
Five out of six birds are down.

939
01:25:34,920 --> 01:25:36,570
Requesting QRT.

940
01:25:38,400 --> 01:25:40,448
Permission to launch second squadron.

941
01:25:41,520 --> 01:25:42,759
Negative, negative.

942
01:25:42,760 --> 01:25:43,807
We don't have any intel about

943
01:25:43,808 --> 01:25:45,882
what other surprises
they could have for us.

944
01:25:47,000 --> 01:25:49,128
Return to base. Return to base. Over.

945
01:25:49,520 --> 01:25:50,442
Roger that.

946
01:25:56,240 --> 01:26:00,211
Banning, are you there? Banning!

947
01:26:04,240 --> 01:26:08,159
Half the White House is just gone.

948
01:26:08,160 --> 01:26:11,079
The residence, the roof,
all destroyed...

949
01:26:11,080 --> 01:26:13,924
and the remainder of
the historic building now trashed.

950
01:26:15,680 --> 01:26:16,806
Speaker Trumbull,

951
01:26:17,800 --> 01:26:20,531
that was a very foolish undertaking.

952
01:26:32,240 --> 01:26:34,083
Your president is next.

953
01:26:34,600 --> 01:26:37,888
You now have one hour
to recall the Seventh Fleet

954
01:26:37,889 --> 01:26:39,319
and your troops.

955
01:26:39,320 --> 01:26:42,608
Once you do so,
I want a helicopter on the North Lawn

956
01:26:42,609 --> 01:26:43,886
fueled and ready.

957
01:26:44,360 --> 01:26:45,771
60 minutes.

958
01:27:05,320 --> 01:27:06,162
Fuck.

959
01:27:07,120 --> 01:27:08,087
It's Banning.

960
01:27:08,640 --> 01:27:09,846
Patch him through.

961
01:27:10,200 --> 01:27:11,645
- Mike?
- Yeah.

962
01:27:12,520 --> 01:27:14,804
We've been trying to reach you, son.
Are you okay?

963
01:27:14,805 --> 01:27:18,521
Mr. Speaker, sir,
if we ever get out of this shit storm...

964
01:27:19,160 --> 01:27:21,162
you can hold me for insubordination.

965
01:27:22,600 --> 01:27:25,166
But your team needs
some serious fucking help.

966
01:27:25,167 --> 01:27:27,242
This is General Clegg,
Army Chief of Staff.

967
01:27:27,243 --> 01:27:29,799
I am ordering you to stand down.

968
01:27:29,800 --> 01:27:31,609
Remove your only eyes and ears
from the ground.

969
01:27:31,610 --> 01:27:32,803
That's fucking brilliant.

970
01:27:32,804 --> 01:27:35,644
We need to pull you out of there
before we lose another hostage!

971
01:27:35,645 --> 01:27:37,879
I am giving you a direct order.

972
01:27:37,880 --> 01:27:41,079
Newsflash, asshole.
I don't work for you.

973
01:27:41,080 --> 01:27:44,319
General Clegg.
I'm the Commander-in-Chief.

974
01:27:44,320 --> 01:27:47,199
If I didn't absolutely need you,
I would relieve you right now.

975
01:27:47,200 --> 01:27:48,690
I will not let this asshole
- General.

976
01:27:48,680 --> 01:27:50,250
- Blow up America, sir!
- I don't wanna here another word...

977
01:27:50,251 --> 01:27:52,561
out of you unless I ask you a question!

978
01:27:57,680 --> 01:27:58,647
Sir.

979
01:27:59,240 --> 01:28:00,446
Mr. Banning.

980
01:28:01,680 --> 01:28:03,125
Mr. Banning, are you there?

981
01:28:05,360 --> 01:28:06,771
Yes, sir. What's the plan?

982
01:28:08,360 --> 01:28:12,682
We're recalling the Seventh Fleet
pulling our troops back from the DMZ

983
01:28:12,683 --> 01:28:14,282
and giving them the helicopter.

984
01:28:14,283 --> 01:28:18,363
Sir, you cannot do that.
You cannot give this guy what he wants.

985
01:28:18,364 --> 01:28:20,521
I've dealt with
these types of men before.

986
01:28:20,522 --> 01:28:22,644
Give me some time. Let me flush him out.

987
01:28:22,645 --> 01:28:26,606
We are talking about the safety
of the President of the United States!

988
01:28:26,607 --> 01:28:28,921
We're talking about a hell of
a lot more than that, sir.

989
01:28:33,560 --> 01:28:36,962
With all due respect,
you're acting president now.

990
01:28:37,840 --> 01:28:39,763
And I'm the best hope you've got.

991
01:28:42,040 --> 01:28:44,168
Okay, Mike.You've got 30 minutes.

992
01:28:49,320 --> 01:28:51,209
Leah, call for you on the landline.

993
01:28:51,210 --> 01:28:52,531
The emergency line.

994
01:28:56,400 --> 01:28:58,004
Can you make sure he gets some morphine?

995
01:28:58,005 --> 01:28:58,808
Yes.

996
01:29:02,120 --> 01:29:03,007
Mike?

997
01:29:03,520 --> 01:29:05,568
Hey. I was just checking in.

998
01:29:07,200 --> 01:29:09,441
Babe. How's your day been?

999
01:29:11,080 --> 01:29:12,525
Yeah, it's been busy.

1000
01:29:13,440 --> 01:29:15,090
It's good, you know.

1001
01:29:16,560 --> 01:29:17,891
How 'bout you?

1002
01:29:18,920 --> 01:29:21,287
Yeah.Busy.

1003
01:29:22,240 --> 01:29:23,651
Hey, you okay?

1004
01:29:24,120 --> 01:29:27,602
Yeah, I just, I've, I've had to stay
a little later than I expected.

1005
01:29:28,840 --> 01:29:30,126
Yeah, me too.

1006
01:29:32,520 --> 01:29:34,727
You're gonna come home tonight, right?

1007
01:29:35,120 --> 01:29:36,959
Yeah. Sure.

1008
01:29:36,960 --> 01:29:38,724
We got a date, remember?

1009
01:29:39,440 --> 01:29:40,851
Hey, I gotta go.

1010
01:29:41,160 --> 01:29:44,767
You know, this, uh,
paperwork's piling up.

1011
01:29:45,240 --> 01:29:46,366
Okay.

1012
01:29:49,680 --> 01:29:50,727
I love you.

1013
01:30:11,560 --> 01:30:12,925
What's the matter, Kang?

1014
01:30:13,320 --> 01:30:15,084
You look like you've seen a ghost.

1015
01:30:15,680 --> 01:30:18,411
I guess you don't know
who you can trust, huh?

1016
01:30:18,412 --> 01:30:19,559
It's over.

1017
01:30:19,560 --> 01:30:23,359
No more televised executions.
No chopper.

1018
01:30:23,360 --> 01:30:24,962
No more negotiating with you

1019
01:30:24,963 --> 01:30:27,930
and the United People's Front
of Who Gives a Fuck.

1020
01:30:28,760 --> 01:30:30,888
I will send the president out...

1021
01:30:30,889 --> 01:30:32,799
one piece at a time.

1022
01:30:32,800 --> 01:30:34,006
It won't matter.

1023
01:30:34,400 --> 01:30:36,524
Because whatever you think
you accomplished

1024
01:30:36,525 --> 01:30:38,284
you won't be alive to see it.

1025
01:30:39,880 --> 01:30:41,166
Shut him down.

1026
01:30:41,640 --> 01:30:44,007
Ah, you're not shutting me down, Kang.

1027
01:30:44,008 --> 01:30:45,799
I'm here to stay.

1028
01:30:45,800 --> 01:30:47,359
I underestimated you.

1029
01:30:47,360 --> 01:30:49,079
It will not happen again.

1030
01:30:49,080 --> 01:30:50,439
There is no again.

1031
01:30:50,440 --> 01:30:54,047
You're gonna die down there alone
cut off from the rest of the world.

1032
01:30:54,048 --> 01:30:57,679
My advice?
Save the last bullet for yourself.

1033
01:30:57,680 --> 01:30:59,199
'Cause if you don't...

1034
01:30:59,200 --> 01:31:01,726
I'm gonna stick my knife
through your brain.

1035
01:31:02,040 --> 01:31:03,359
But don't worry.

1036
01:31:03,360 --> 01:31:06,006
I'm gonna leak the photos
of your body to the press.

1037
01:31:06,007 --> 01:31:08,321
You know, 'cause I know you
like that kind of shit.

1038
01:31:27,280 --> 01:31:28,122
Her!

1039
01:31:47,000 --> 01:31:49,679
I pledge allegiance to the flag...

1040
01:31:49,680 --> 01:31:54,402
of the United States of America!

1041
01:32:08,880 --> 01:32:10,928
Your leader is out of his mind.

1042
01:32:15,280 --> 01:32:17,521
You fucking idiot!

1043
01:32:23,360 --> 01:32:24,327
Go.

1044
01:32:24,880 --> 01:32:26,120
Walk.

1045
01:32:26,920 --> 01:32:28,081
Move!

1046
01:32:54,600 --> 01:32:57,206
Sir, there's movement
in front of the White House.

1047
01:32:57,207 --> 01:32:58,599
Ours or theirs?

1048
01:32:58,600 --> 01:33:00,523
Looks like Secretary McMillan, sir.

1049
01:33:00,524 --> 01:33:02,887
- Any bulges, wires?
- Negative.

1050
01:33:08,680 --> 01:33:11,206
Sir, ground reports activity
at the White House.

1051
01:33:11,720 --> 01:33:13,279
- Is that?
- McMillan.

1052
01:33:13,280 --> 01:33:16,966
Get a team out there now.
And another to cover! Go!

1053
01:33:20,560 --> 01:33:24,451
It looks like Secretary McMillan.
Yeah, yes, it is.

1054
01:33:46,000 --> 01:33:46,967
Yes!

1055
01:34:02,280 --> 01:34:03,202
Mike?

1056
01:34:05,560 --> 01:34:06,439
Hey.

1057
01:34:06,440 --> 01:34:08,761
He got away. He's back in the bunker.

1058
01:34:09,600 --> 01:34:12,365
You gave it a good shot, Mike.
You saved McMillan.

1059
01:34:13,840 --> 01:34:17,204
North and South Korean military
forces are onhigh alert

1060
01:34:17,205 --> 01:34:20,283
in response to rumors
of an impending American

1061
01:34:20,284 --> 01:34:22,039
pull-out from the DMZ.

1062
01:34:22,040 --> 01:34:25,282
India, China and Russia
have declared a state of emergency

1063
01:34:25,283 --> 01:34:27,119
and have mobilized military forces.

1064
01:34:27,120 --> 01:34:27,962
In the Middle East though,

1065
01:34:27,963 --> 01:34:31,165
the response to the attack
on the White House is jubilant.

1066
01:34:31,166 --> 01:34:33,639
Crowds of thousands
are celebrating in the streets

1067
01:34:33,640 --> 01:34:35,402
and American flags are burning.

1068
01:34:35,403 --> 01:34:37,926
...created by a U.S. departure
could spark

1069
01:34:37,927 --> 01:34:42,879
an immediate and full-scale conflict
and that any conventional war

1070
01:34:42,880 --> 01:34:45,565
in this heavily-armed corner
of the world

1071
01:34:45,566 --> 01:34:50,122
could easily escalate
into nuclear confrontation.

1072
01:34:50,400 --> 01:34:51,526
The hour's up.

1073
01:34:52,320 --> 01:34:53,924
Send the helicopter.

1074
01:34:55,680 --> 01:34:57,409
Le's recall the Seventh Fleet.

1075
01:34:59,320 --> 01:35:01,519
Pull the troops out of the DMZ.

1076
01:35:01,520 --> 01:35:03,363
We just lost South Korea.

1077
01:35:05,680 --> 01:35:07,761
Our Pentagon sources are now saying

1078
01:35:07,762 --> 01:35:08,921
that U.S. ground troops

1079
01:35:08,922 --> 01:35:11,651
have been given the order
to withdraw from Korea

1080
01:35:11,652 --> 01:35:14,039
for the first time in 60 years.

1081
01:35:14,040 --> 01:35:16,643
We're also hearing reports
that the U.S.'s Seventh Fleet

1082
01:35:16,644 --> 01:35:19,243
has been directed to pull back
in the region.

1083
01:35:19,244 --> 01:35:20,646
Although unconfirmed,

1084
01:35:20,647 --> 01:35:23,765
this historic turn of events
seems to be motivated

1085
01:35:23,766 --> 01:35:26,124
by today's attack on the White House

1086
01:35:26,125 --> 01:35:28,643
which began
as the Prime Minister of Korea

1087
01:35:28,644 --> 01:35:30,722
was meeting with President Asher.

1088
01:35:55,280 --> 01:35:56,202
What are they doing?

1089
01:36:33,560 --> 01:36:35,961
Mike. We have to get Kang
and the president out

1090
01:36:35,962 --> 01:36:37,962
in the open and take out our best shot.

1091
01:36:37,963 --> 01:36:39,041
Copy that, sir.

1092
01:36:53,440 --> 01:36:55,283
Bravo Team is in position.

1093
01:36:58,440 --> 01:37:01,171
Sir, we are ready.
All units are in position.

1094
01:37:08,600 --> 01:37:09,886
Here come the hostages.

1095
01:37:14,520 --> 01:37:16,249
We count 11 targets, sir.

1096
01:37:16,760 --> 01:37:18,442
One of them's gotta be the president.

1097
01:37:18,443 --> 01:37:19,601
That's their ticket out.

1098
01:37:24,680 --> 01:37:26,762
Hercules Six in position.

1099
01:37:27,200 --> 01:37:28,770
Can you I.D. the president?

1100
01:37:31,760 --> 01:37:32,807
Negative.

1101
01:37:33,240 --> 01:37:34,765
Can you I.D. Kang?

1102
01:37:37,040 --> 01:37:37,919
Negative.

1103
01:37:37,920 --> 01:37:39,206
Targets unclear.

1104
01:37:41,400 --> 01:37:43,125
Sir, all ground units are in position.

1105
01:37:43,126 --> 01:37:45,282
Do we have the go-ahead to take them?

1106
01:37:55,000 --> 01:37:56,684
If we're gonna go, we gotta go now, sir.

1107
01:38:00,920 --> 01:38:02,410
Do we have the go-ahead, sir?

1108
01:38:05,680 --> 01:38:08,331
No. Too risky.
They could kill the president.

1109
01:38:10,800 --> 01:38:11,562
Yes, sir.

1110
01:38:12,160 --> 01:38:14,200
It's okay.
We have a tracking device on the chopper.

1111
01:38:27,400 --> 01:38:30,199
Holy shit. What was that? Was that us?

1112
01:38:30,200 --> 01:38:32,328
Negative, negative. That wasn't us.

1113
01:38:40,600 --> 01:38:44,039
Though it is not confirmed yet,
President Asher

1114
01:38:44,040 --> 01:38:45,925
is believed to have been
among those killed

1115
01:38:45,926 --> 01:38:48,001
when the Blackhawk helicopter went down

1116
01:38:48,002 --> 01:38:50,241
in flames on the White House North Lawn.

1117
01:38:51,640 --> 01:38:54,642
And certainly, today's events
will be recorded in history

1118
01:38:54,643 --> 01:38:57,405
- as one of this country's darkest hours.
- Oh, my God.

1119
01:39:00,640 --> 01:39:02,165
The president's gone.

1120
01:39:20,880 --> 01:39:21,927
Mike?

1121
01:39:22,520 --> 01:39:23,931
What the hell just happened?

1122
01:39:25,040 --> 01:39:26,644
I'm sorry to report...

1123
01:39:28,160 --> 01:39:30,447
the president was on that helicopter.

1124
01:39:31,160 --> 01:39:32,446
And Kang?

1125
01:39:33,200 --> 01:39:35,039
Kang killed himself.

1126
01:39:35,040 --> 01:39:36,929
And all the other hostages.

1127
01:39:38,800 --> 01:39:43,124
Wait. This doesn't add up.

1128
01:39:44,280 --> 01:39:45,879
It doesn't make sense.

1129
01:39:45,880 --> 01:39:47,325
What doesn't make sense?

1130
01:39:48,720 --> 01:39:50,801
Kang would not go out like that, sir.

1131
01:39:50,802 --> 01:39:52,165
That's not who he is.

1132
01:39:54,000 --> 01:39:56,124
I think he's still in the bunker.

1133
01:39:56,125 --> 01:39:58,691
And he has the president.
He's gonna try and slip away.

1134
01:39:59,040 --> 01:40:01,042
If Kang is still on the premises
with the president,

1135
01:40:01,043 --> 01:40:02,849
you can't let him leave.

1136
01:40:04,360 --> 01:40:05,441
He won't.

1137
01:40:07,320 --> 01:40:10,051
Huh? Who the hell does that?

1138
01:40:11,360 --> 01:40:12,327
Enough!

1139
01:40:15,960 --> 01:40:18,559
I read your Bible, Mr. President.

1140
01:40:18,560 --> 01:40:21,719
It says, the wages of sin is death.

1141
01:40:21,720 --> 01:40:23,370
You better keep that in mind.

1142
01:40:31,920 --> 01:40:32,728
What are you doing?

1143
01:40:32,729 --> 01:40:34,639
Cerberus has been activated.

1144
01:40:34,640 --> 01:40:36,369
We haven't launched any missiles yet.

1145
01:40:38,120 --> 01:40:39,929
I don't need to launch them.

1146
01:40:40,360 --> 01:40:43,006
The explosive force
within each hardened silo

1147
01:40:43,007 --> 01:40:44,570
will detonate the missiles.

1148
01:40:44,960 --> 01:40:47,406
Tens of millions of Americans
will perish.

1149
01:40:48,120 --> 01:40:51,966
Your country will be a
cold, dark nuclear wasteland.

1150
01:40:54,840 --> 01:40:58,640
Now, too, America shall know
suffering and famine.

1151
01:41:00,880 --> 01:41:03,925
South Korean officials are saying
now that they've pulled out the reserves

1152
01:41:03,926 --> 01:41:06,844
and they're mobilizing additional
armored units in response...

1153
01:41:06,845 --> 01:41:09,439
Sir? Cerberus has been activated.

1154
01:41:09,440 --> 01:41:11,408
- What?
- NORAD confirms.

1155
01:41:12,840 --> 01:41:14,519
How did it come to this?

1156
01:41:14,520 --> 01:41:16,799
We lost Korea and now our nukes?

1157
01:41:16,800 --> 01:41:18,926
- They couldn't have broken the code.
- That would be impossible.

1158
01:41:18,927 --> 01:41:21,399
They'd be on the bunker computer
for days to break three codes.

1159
01:41:21,400 --> 01:41:23,919
No, he only need to break one code.

1160
01:41:23,920 --> 01:41:26,207
But we haven't launched any missiles.

1161
01:41:29,720 --> 01:41:31,848
They're gonna detonate them
in their silos.

1162
01:41:34,520 --> 01:41:35,646
How many?

1163
01:41:38,080 --> 01:41:39,286
All of 'em.

1164
01:41:47,280 --> 01:41:49,328
He's just opened the gates of hell.

1165
01:41:53,960 --> 01:41:55,405
Time to go, Mr. President!

1166
01:42:05,280 --> 01:42:07,647
You really think you're gonna
get out of here alive?

1167
01:42:08,320 --> 01:42:10,209
The world thinks we're both dead.

1168
01:42:11,440 --> 01:42:13,329
And with you as insurance...

1169
01:44:09,920 --> 01:44:11,046
Come on, Mike.

1170
01:44:17,160 --> 01:44:19,128
Looks like you failed again, Mike.

1171
01:44:46,640 --> 01:44:47,527
Sir?

1172
01:44:48,000 --> 01:44:51,800
Sir, sir, look at me. Sir...

1173
01:44:53,880 --> 01:44:54,881
Sir.

1174
01:44:55,920 --> 01:45:00,079
Okay. It's gone through
and you've lost a little blood.

1175
01:45:00,080 --> 01:45:01,764
But I'm gonna get you outta here, okay?

1176
01:45:02,520 --> 01:45:03,806
Now, you know what to do.

1177
01:45:06,000 --> 01:45:07,206
Ben, Ben, come on!

1178
01:45:07,207 --> 01:45:09,039
- Cerberus.
- What?

1179
01:45:09,040 --> 01:45:10,565
Cerberus activated.

1180
01:45:10,960 --> 01:45:12,121
Cerberus.

1181
01:45:14,920 --> 01:45:16,251
Keep that pressed in.

1182
01:45:16,252 --> 01:45:17,685
Sir! Ben!

1183
01:45:18,160 --> 01:45:19,525
You're gonna be okay.

1184
01:45:19,526 --> 01:45:20,362
All right.

1185
01:45:29,880 --> 01:45:31,039
This is Banning.

1186
01:45:31,040 --> 01:45:33,164
I have the president.
He's hurt, but alive.

1187
01:45:33,165 --> 01:45:34,924
How do I switch this fucking thing off?

1188
01:45:35,400 --> 01:45:37,289
- Hang on.
- Deactivation code!

1189
01:45:38,960 --> 01:45:42,726
Find a control panel marked,
"Countermand."

1190
01:45:43,760 --> 01:45:44,727
Countermand.

1191
01:45:45,560 --> 01:45:46,559
Got it!

1192
01:45:46,560 --> 01:45:51,202
Flip a blue-white switch marked,
"Initiate Recall."

1193
01:45:51,760 --> 01:45:53,205
Initiate recall.

1194
01:45:53,960 --> 01:45:54,688
Okay.

1195
01:45:55,160 --> 01:45:57,879
Deactivation sequence initiated.

1196
01:45:57,880 --> 01:45:59,403
Please enter abort command.

1197
01:45:59,404 --> 01:46:00,811
Come on, come on, come on, come on!

1198
01:46:01,320 --> 01:46:03,163
November. India.

1199
01:46:04,960 --> 01:46:06,119
Lima.

1200
01:46:06,120 --> 01:46:09,999
- Wait, wait. Yep.
- 5-Oscar-hotel.

1201
01:46:10,000 --> 01:46:12,759
- Oscar, hotel.
- Backslash. Niner.

1202
01:46:12,760 --> 01:46:14,808
- Backslash.
- Victor. Kilo.

1203
01:46:15,240 --> 01:46:16,639
- Hash-tag.
- What?

1204
01:46:16,640 --> 01:46:18,847
- Hash-tag.
- Shift 3!

1205
01:46:19,320 --> 01:46:20,599
Okay, fuck!

1206
01:46:20,600 --> 01:46:22,839
- Shift 3!
- Echo.

1207
01:46:22,840 --> 01:46:24,039
Sierra.

1208
01:46:24,040 --> 01:46:25,963
- Foxtrot.
- Foxtrot.

1209
01:46:26,880 --> 01:46:27,839
Is that it?

1210
01:46:27,840 --> 01:46:28,762
That's it.

1211
01:46:34,800 --> 01:46:37,326
Cerberus has been deactivated.

1212
01:46:46,960 --> 01:46:50,079
Sir. NORAD confirms...

1213
01:46:50,080 --> 01:46:51,730
Cerberus has been shut down.

1214
01:46:52,200 --> 01:46:53,326
Good.

1215
01:46:53,760 --> 01:46:56,081
Now get me Seoul and Pyongyang
on the line.

1216
01:47:25,400 --> 01:47:27,004
Are you ready, Mr. President?

1217
01:47:38,280 --> 01:47:39,327
All right.

1218
01:47:55,920 --> 01:47:57,649
Sorry about the house, sir.

1219
01:47:59,880 --> 01:48:03,202
It's okay. I believe it's insured.

1220
01:48:25,360 --> 01:48:26,930
We've lost good friends.

1221
01:48:28,920 --> 01:48:30,046
Family.

1222
01:48:31,920 --> 01:48:33,206
All good people.

1223
01:48:36,040 --> 01:48:38,327
- Heroes, every one of them.
- Dad!

1224
01:48:39,320 --> 01:48:42,130
Our hearts and prayers
go out to their families.

1225
01:48:42,880 --> 01:48:44,450
And they will be remembered.

1226
01:48:45,560 --> 01:48:47,199
Nor will we forget...

1227
01:48:47,200 --> 01:48:50,319
those who serve out of the spotlight

1228
01:48:50,320 --> 01:48:54,006
to whom we owe our highest gratitude.

1229
01:49:01,320 --> 01:49:05,166
Our foe did not come only to destroy
our things or our people.

1230
01:49:06,160 --> 01:49:08,719
They came to desecrate a way of life.

1231
01:49:08,720 --> 01:49:11,883
To foul our beliefs,
trample our freedom.

1232
01:49:12,320 --> 01:49:14,846
And in this, not only did they fail...

1233
01:49:15,360 --> 01:49:18,330
they granted us the greatest gift.

1234
01:49:19,600 --> 01:49:21,443
A chance at our rebirth.

1235
01:49:23,760 --> 01:49:26,570
We will rise.Renewed.

1236
01:49:27,040 --> 01:49:29,088
Stronger and united.

1237
01:49:29,600 --> 01:49:30,931
This is our time...

1238
01:49:31,640 --> 01:49:35,929
our chance to get back
to the best of who we are.

1239
01:49:36,760 --> 01:49:39,359
To lead by example with the dignity,

1240
01:49:39,360 --> 01:49:42,125
integrity and honor
that built this country

1241
01:49:42,800 --> 01:49:45,724
and which will build it once again.

1242
01:49:46,080 --> 01:49:47,411
May God bless you.

1243
01:49:48,560 --> 01:49:51,211
And may God bless
the United States of America.
